title: cAdvisor Pods/Containers: Traffic and Status of Network Interface
agents: prometheus
catalog: containerization/cadvisor
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:

 This check monitors the operational status, traffic, packet counts,
 discards and errors of network interfaces of containers and/or pods.

 This check obtains its metrics values through Prometheus. In order to allow
 generation of cAdvisor related CPU services, the user needs to enable
 the cAdvisor option under the Prometheus Datasource Programs ruleset.

item:
 One summarized check of all network information

discovery:
 One service is created for each network interface.
